{"tid":334233,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"同屋企人旅行真係。。。","createTime":"2017-07-24T13:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T01:13:03.000Z","uid":102788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66a64acf7a06a5a64c95462d6ee5ffd9fce5009b","tid":334233,"uid":102788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"今日同屋企人去咗廣島原爆個度參觀<br />\n我老母突然爆左句：日本抵死啦 ！係心口應該痴個反日兩個字！<br />\n我即刻燥咗 就話：你反日又嚟？<br />\n之後佢就屌我話我無禮貌又話我發脾氣<br />\n又話歷史係咁架啦。。。<br />\n<br />\n仲有三日旅程點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係人地個博物館大大聲咁講真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50df853018888c9316c046643d2627f1210e550f","tid":334233,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"日本應該無人識聽佢講咩既"},{"pid":"5abfffe436ede056fef2abc7661cc73f2356c206","tid":334233,"uid":128916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T19:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本應該無人識聽佢講咩既</blockquote><br />\n如果有人聽得明 都幾失禮下"},{"pid":"75c101c1794d33ed7818e936af45c7f74b29a411","tid":334233,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:27:42.000Z","msg":"我老豆都會咁<br />\n之後我會大大聲屌到佢反皮<br />\n是咪好不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a376c0c159712979c789885986eeb9a4e6f979","tid":334233,"uid":41914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"咁佢地用咩心態去日本.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁憎既話, 一開始就唔好同地去呢D地方, 去其他地方會唔會仲好D呢<br />\n<br />\n我屋企都有一個&quot;中國人&quot;, 我唔會同佢去日本, 亦唔會同佢講政治野, 因為我知道大家根本傾唔埋, 晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}